<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-09-0910 </DOCNO><TEXT>This bibliography contains citations concerning methods of removing asbestosfrom buildings and water. Walk-through survey reports describe wet- anddry-removal techniques being employed at work sites. Containment barriers,ventilation systems, and vacuum systems used during asbestos-removalprojects are also described. Monitors that measure asbestos dust fibers,and water filters that remove asbestos are also discussed. Alternativeuses in highways and as an absorbing agent in oil spill cleanups areexplored along with disposal methods. (This updated bibliography contains91 citations, 11 of which are new entries to the previous edition.)</TEXT></DOC>